By":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時就係怕轉運會整唔見件貨先至會靠onlineshop<br />\n明知貨價係幾多 就係自己怕煩所以比人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係限量/好難買 我都唔會益代購<br />\n又要受氣又要等勁耐 最多平20-30蚊<br />\n但佢地一件貨已經賺40-50蚊 好好搵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求人不如求己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫襯代購要受氣表表姐就係水魚嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點解要貼錢買難受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 埋呢次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，會focus翻beauty topic"},{"pid":"f075b65e536c10cb19c4cf099a91a7797247d3d3","tid":9194,"uid":36380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef4b5507666085ed81a74b31bfb1433d5bb0350e","tid":9194,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無sis用過費洛蒙香水？有無用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過 molecule 01，男朋友難得會讚我浸味香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過無用過ig shop果d"},{"pid":"60688d6a58ee50db30e4f96a1c1b9c1de2c9bd34","tid":9194,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"絲打不如我地唔好再用88啦，lihk新post就跟住2，3去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ca4474304a2c8c7245db2e487a608053bfb4f4","tid":9194,"uid":36251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"最後都係裝左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bf598b9ccbeb298e931702be8e28fd48a5f397","tid":9194,"uid":7645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打不如我地唔好再用88啦，lihk新post就跟住2，3去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n趁而呢個post仲新，不如而加開返？"},{"pi